.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-HTLC-COUNT-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-htlc-count-max \- FEAT-2538 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-htlc-count-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
peer-htlc-count-max for lightning CLI (FEAT-2538).
.PP
Returns the peer with the highest total HTLC count across their channels.
Output: JSON from CLN with key htlc_count.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
